Homage to RohithThe city unit of CPI(M) held a candle light vigil was held near the Gandhiji statue opposite GVMC main office here on Wednesday to pay homage to Central University of Hyderabad research scholar Rohith Vemula who had committed suicide. State secretariat member of the party Ch. Narasinga Rao and others said Vice-Chancellor of CHU and Union Minister Bandaru Dattatreya were responsible for Rohith’s suicide and they should be sacked . Suspension of four other Dalit students should be removed and the government must support Rohith’s family and conduct a impartial inquiry, the party demanded.